Stack: HTML/CSS/JS, Three.js, Vercel/GitHub. No npm, no frameworks.
Two coordinate systems: Global (Three.js, -Z=True North) and Design (user-set via designNorthAngle).
Two viewports: 2D plan and 3D perspective. North point compass shared between both.
LAI database (LAI_categorised.csv) is core IP -- never expose or send to external APIs.
Use Microsoft Edge for development -- Chrome has rendering issues.

